<!-- ═══ COMPANY HISTORY ═══ -->
<template id="page_history" name="CR Farm — History">
    <t t-call="website.layout">
        <t t-set="title">Our History | CR Farm Products</t>

        <section style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a5c2a,#2e8b47); color:#fff;" class="py-5">
            <div class="container text-center">
                <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold">Our History</h1>
                <p class="lead opacity-90 mt-2">A family legacy rooted in the land of San Carlos, Costa Rica</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="py-5">
            <div class="container" style="max-width:800px;">

                <div class="row g-0 mb-5">
                    <div class="col-auto text-center" style="width:80px;">
                        <div class="rounded-circle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mx-auto mb-2" style="width:52px;height:52px;background:#2e8b47;color:#fff;font-weight:bold;font-size:.8rem;">Roots</div>
                        <div style="height:100%;width:2px;background:#d0e8d4;margin:0 auto;min-height:60px;"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col ps-4 pb-5">
                        <h4 class="fw-bold" style="color:#1a5c2a;">Generational Roots</h4>
                        <p>Our agricultural story began long before the company was founded. The founder's grandparents and great-grandparents cultivated deep ties to the land in the verdant valleys of San Carlos, Alajuela — one of Costa Rica's most productive agricultural regions. This love of farming and the land was passed down through each generation.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row g-0 mb-5">
                    <div class="col-auto text-center" style="width:80px;">
                        <div class="rounded-circle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mx-auto mb-2" style="width:52px;height:52px;background:#2e8b47;color:#fff;font-weight:bold;">2005</div>
                        <div style="height:100%;width:2px;background:#d0e8d4;margin:0 auto;min-height:60px;"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col ps-4 pb-5">
                        <h4 class="fw-bold" style="color:#1a5c2a;">2005 — CR Farm Products Is Born</h4>
                        <p>Four brothers decided to formalize the family's agricultural legacy and founded <strong>CR Farm Products</strong>. The company's first exports were <strong>ginger and squash</strong> to buyers in the United States. The positive market response validated the vision: high-quality Costa Rican tropical products had strong international demand.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row g-0 mb-5">
                    <div class="col-auto text-center" style="width:80px;">
                        <div class="rounded-circle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mx-auto mb-2" style="width:52px;height:52px;background:#2e8b47;color:#fff;font-weight:bold;font-size:.85rem;">2008+</div>
                        <div style="height:100%;width:2px;background:#d0e8d4;margin:0 auto;min-height:60px;"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col ps-4 pb-5">
                        <h4 class="fw-bold" style="color:#1a5c2a;">Expansion: Cassava, Eddoes &amp; Malanga</h4>
                        <p>The product portfolio expanded significantly. Cassava (yuca) and eddoes (ñampi) became the flagship exports, complemented by malanga lila, malanga blanca, malanga isleña, ñame and other tropical roots. Each product was carefully selected for its international market appeal and CR Farm's capacity to supply consistently.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row g-0 mb-5">
                    <div class="col-auto text-center" style="width:80px;">
                        <div class="rounded-circle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mx-auto mb-2" style="width:52px;height:52px;background:#2e8b47;color:#fff;font-weight:bold;font-size:.85rem;">Europe</div>
                        <div style="height:100%;width:2px;background:#d0e8d4;margin:0 auto;min-height:60px;"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col ps-4 pb-5">
                        <h4 class="fw-bold" style="color:#1a5c2a;">Reaching Europe</h4>
                        <p>CR Farm Products expanded its export routes to <strong>France, Spain, the Netherlands and the United Kingdom</strong>, tapping into the growing demand from Caribbean and Latin American diaspora communities across Europe. Customized packaging formats were developed for each market's specific requirements.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row g-0 mb-5">
                    <div class="col-auto text-center" style="width:80px;">
                        <div class="rounded-circle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mx-auto mb-2" style="width:52px;height:52px;background:#2e8b47;color:#fff;font-weight:bold;font-size:.8rem;">Cert.</div>
                        <div style="height:100%;width:2px;background:#d0e8d4;margin:0 auto;min-height:60px;"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col ps-4 pb-5">
                        <h4 class="fw-bold" style="color:#1a5c2a;">International Certifications</h4>
                        <p>CR Farm Products achieved <strong>GLOBALG.A.P.</strong> certification, the international benchmark for food safety and sustainable farming. This milestone was followed by the <strong>Esencial Costa Rica</strong> country brand certification and recognition as a <strong>PYME</strong> (certified SME) for sustainable growth and local agricultural development.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row g-0">
                    <div class="col-auto text-center" style="width:80px;">
                        <div class="rounded-circle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mx-auto" style="width:52px;height:52px;background:#f0a500;color:#fff;font-weight:bold;">Now</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col ps-4">
                        <h4 class="fw-bold" style="color:#1a5c2a;">Today — Still Growing</h4>
                        <p>CR Farm Products continues to grow from its roots in San Carlos, Costa Rica. With offices also in <strong>Miami, Florida</strong>, we serve buyers across three continents. We operate with modern ERP systems for full traceability, renewable energy in our facilities, and a team as committed to excellence as the brothers who started it all in 2005.</p>
                        <p class="fw-semibold" style="color:#2e8b47;">"We Harvest for You &amp; Your Family's Health" — and always will.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="py-4 text-center" style="background:#f8fdf9;">
            <div class="container">
                <a href="/crfarm/contact" class="btn btn-success px-5">Become Part of Our Story →</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </t>
</template>


