                                <div class="col-md-4 text-center d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
                                    <div style="font-size:5rem;">🌱</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Ñampi -->
                    <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-4">
                        <div class="card-body p-4">
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-md-8">
                                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-1" style="color:#1a5c2a;">Ñampi / Eddoes</h4>
                                    <p class="text-muted small mb-2"><em>Colocasia esculenta</em> · Tariff: 071450100011</p>
                                    <p>CR Farm's specialty and a cornerstone export. Ñampi (small taro) is highly popular in Caribbean and West African diaspora communities worldwide.</p>
                                    <div class="row g-2 small">
                                        <div class="col-6"><span class="text-success fw-bold">📅 Season:</span> Year-round</div>
                                        <div class="col-6"><span class="text-success fw-bold">📦 Europe:</span> 10 kg boxes</div>
                                        <div class="col-6"><span class="text-success fw-bold">📦 USA/Canada:</span> 13.65–16 kg</div>
                                        <div class="col-6"><span class="text-success fw-bold">⚖️ Small-Med:</span> 80–120 g</div>
                                        <div class="col-6"><span class="text-success fw-bold">⚖️ Large:</span> 120 g+</div>
                                        <div class="col-6"><span class="text-success fw-bold">🪵 Pallet:</span> 60–100 boxes</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-4 text-center d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
                                    <div style="font-size:5rem;">🫚</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Malanga group -->
                    <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-4">
                        <div class="card-body p-4">
                            <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3" style="color:#1a5c2a;">Malanga / Taro Varieties</h4>
                            <p class="text-muted small mb-3">Season: November – May &nbsp;·&nbsp; Tariff: 071450100011 &nbsp;·&nbsp; 60 boxes/pallet &nbsp;·&nbsp; 20-22 pallets/container</p>
                            <div class="row g-3">
                                <div class="col-md-4">
                                    <div class="border rounded p-3">
                                        <h6 class="fw-bold mb-1">Malanga Lila</h6>
                                        <p class="small text-muted mb-1"><em>Xanthosoma sagittifolium</em></p>
                                        <p class="small mb-0">Also: Purple Tiquisque, Purple Yautia. 1st class min. 15 cm / 2nd class 10-15 cm.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-4">
                                    <div class="border rounded p-3">
                                        <h6 class="fw-bold mb-1">Malanga Blanca</h6>
                                        <p class="small text-muted mb-1"><em>Xanthosoma sagittifolium</em></p>
                                        <p class="small mb-0">Also: Tiquisque Blanco, Yautia Blanca. Same specs as Lila.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-4">
                                    <div class="border rounded p-3">
                                        <h6 class="fw-bold mb-1">Malanga Isleña</h6>
                                        <p class="small text-muted mb-1"><em>Colocasia esculenta</em></p>
                                        <p class="small mb-0">Weight range 400 g – 2 kg. Highly demanded in Caribbean markets.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-4">
                                    <div class="border rounded p-3">
                                        <h6 class="fw-bold mb-1">Big Taro / Malanga Coco</h6>
                                        <p class="small text-muted mb-1"><em>Colocasia esculenta</em> (variant)</p>
                                        <p class="small mb-0">Large-size taro preferred in Asian and Caribbean specialty markets.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-4">
                                    <div class="border rounded p-3">
                                        <h6 class="fw-bold mb-1">Ñame / White Yam</h6>
                                        <p class="small text-muted mb-1">Tropical yam</p>
                                        <p class="small mb-0">Staple root with strong demand in Caribbean and African communities in Europe and USA.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-4">
                                    <div class="border rounded p-3">
                                        <h6 class="fw-bold mb-1">Yampi / Chinese Papa</h6>
                                        <p class="small text-muted mb-1">Asian-origin yam</p>
                                        <p class="small mb-0">Popular in Asian and Caribbean specialty food markets across North America.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Dynamic categories from crfp.product -->
                <t t-foreach="product_groups" t-as="cat_key">
                    <t t-if="cat_key != 'tubers'">
                        <div t-att-id="cat_key" class="mb-5">
                            <h2 class="fw-bold border-bottom pb-2 mb-4" style="color:#1a5c2a;">
                                <t t-if="cat_key == 'coconut'">🥥 </t>
                                <t t-elif="cat_key == 'sugar_cane'">🎋 </t>
                                <t t-else="">🥦 </t>
                                <t t-esc="product_groups[cat_key]['label']"/>
                            </h2>
                            <div class="row g-3">
                                <t t-foreach="product_groups[cat_key]['products']" t-as="product">
                                    <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
                                        <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm p-3">
                                            <h6 class="fw-bold mb-1" style="color:#1a5c2a;">
                                                <t t-esc="product.name"/>
                                            </h6>
                                            <t t-if="product.net_kg">
                                                <span class="badge bg-light text-dark border small">
                                                    <t t-esc="product.net_kg"/> kg/box
                                                </span>
                                            </t>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </t>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </t>
                </t>

                <div class="text-center mt-4 p-4 rounded" style="background:#f8fdf9;">
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-2" style="color:#1a5c2a;">Don't see what you're looking for?</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-3">We work with a wide range of products. Contact us and we'll check availability.</p>
                    <a href="/crfarm/contact" class="btn btn-success px-4">Check Availability</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </t>
</template>


